## Slash command descriptions and context menu names
## Used by FluentTranslator for Discord's built-in command localization

# Slash command descriptions
cmd-desc-ping = Get a quick reply from the bot to see if it is online.
cmd-desc-invite = Prints an invitation to add ReQuest to your server.
cmd-desc-support = Prints the bot version and a link to the development server.
cmd-desc-language = Set your preferred language for bot responses.
cmd-desc-help = Displays a list of commands and their functions.
cmd-desc-admin = Administration wizard. Bot owner only
cmd-desc-config = Server Configuration Menus (Server Admins only)
cmd-desc-gm = Game Master Menus
cmd-desc-player = Player Menus
cmd-desc-shop = Opens a shop in the current channel if one is configured.

# Context menu names
cmd-context-name-trade = Trade
cmd-context-name-modify-player = Modify Player
cmd-context-name-view-player = View Player
